item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: swamiBE
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.title: Sample Page
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my blog. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

item.excerpt:encoded:
This uniquely designed bi-fold wallet is handcrafted from a single piece of leather which can be easily flattened for tanning and oiling. The raw leather starts out a light color and will age and darken as it absorbs the oils from your hands and is exposed to the sun. The more you use it, the better it looks. Features:
- large bill slot (will fit almost any currency worldwide) - two interior pouches that can hold up to 12 cards each - inside flaps great for holding receipts - 4oz vegetable tanned leather - dimensions: 3.5" x 4.5" and .6" thick (will thin out with use) - handcrafted in the USA
Please note: Wallet will drastically thin out over time.

item.excerpt:encoded:
Let's face it. Most people carry around a lot of excess in their wallets. For those who prefer a more minimal approach, this slim card case is perfect for holding just the essentials. This ultra slim design can be comfortably carried in the front or back pocket. Features:
- main pouch (holds up to 5 cards) - back slot for convenient access to your most used card - 4oz vegetable tanned leather and black cordovan leather - dimensions: 4" x 3" and 0.25" thick - handcrafted in the USA
*Please note: Cards may seem to fit very snug at first, but the leather will stretch with use and conform to the amount of cards you carry. Click here for leather care info

item.excerpt:encoded:
We've teamed up with Verde Styles for a special collaboration on our latest product: handmade bamboo sunglasses. Bamboo is one of the fastest growing plants in the world and is eco-friendly, durable and lightweight. Each pair features a laser engraved Ugmonk ampersand on the sides, 1.1 polarized lenses, and comes with a custom bamboo case and microfiber pouch to keep the shades safe when they're not on your head.
- handmade from Bamboo - laser engraved Ugmonk ampersand - custom bamboo case and microfiber pouch - 1.1 polarized lenses - limited edition
